iewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M15 239c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9L207 465c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0s9.4-24.6 0-33.9L65.9 256 241 81c9.4-9.4 9.4-24.6 0-33.9s-24.6-9.4-33.9 0L15 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--next page-right-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M305 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L113 465c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0s-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l175-175L79 81c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9s24.6-9.4 33.9 0L305 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-koiXkd gdYKDS\"></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Meta will also take over Venus Concept's research and manufacturing facility in San Jose, California, and gain the rights to produce NeoGraft systems.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">In return, Meta will grant Venus Concept a perpetual, royalty-free global license covering certain patents included in the transaction.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">CEO <strong>Rajiv De Silva</strong> described the agreement as a step forward in Venus Concept's plan to unlock shareholder value.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-exeBjx kjPTmb raptive-ad-placement mx-auto overflow-hidden min-h-[250px] min-w-[300px] raptive-ad-wrapper flex flex-col items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"raptive-ben-content w-full flex items-center justify-center\" id=\"\"></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">The capital raised is expected to help the firm reduce operating costs, improve cash flow, and enhance focus on its primary aesthetic device business. \"We are confident Meta Healthcare Group will provide the strategic investment and resources needed to maximize the global addressable markets for the ARTAS and NeoGraft technologies.,\" De Silva said.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">In fiscal year 2024, the Venus Hair business contributed approximately $12.5 million in revenue while incurring operational cash usage of around $6.7 million.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Price Action: </strong>VERO shares traded higher by 35.1% to $3.230 at last check Friday.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45821742\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><em><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/markets/market-summary/25/06/45809203/investors-pay-the-price-as-musk-trump-war-of-words-escalates-once-allies-now-foes-their-linked-stocks-crypto-and-funds-wipe-out-155-billion-in-a-single-day\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Investors Pay The Price As Musk-Trump War Of Words Escalates: Once Allies, Now Foes, Their Linked Stocks, Crypto And Funds Wipe Out $155 Billion In A Single Day</a></em></strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Photo via Shutterstock</em></p><!--/$--></div></div>",
